</p>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id=3D"Mechanical_implementation">=
Mechanical implementation</h2><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D=
"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/inde=
x.php?title=3DHill_cipher&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D6" title=3D"Edit =
section: Mechanical implementation"><span>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-=
editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>When operating on 2 symbols at once, a Hill cipher offers no particular =
advantage over <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Playfair_cipher" ti=
tle=3D"Playfair cipher">Playfair</a> or the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia=
.org/wiki/Bifid_cipher" title=3D"Bifid cipher">bifid cipher</a>, and in fac=
t is weaker than either, and slightly more laborious to operate by pencil-a=
nd-paper. As the dimension increases, the cipher rapidly becomes infeasible=
 for a human to operate by hand.
</p><p>A Hill cipher of dimension 6 was implemented mechanically. Hill and =
a partner were awarded a <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patent" t=
itle=3D"Patent">patent</a> (<span><a rel=3D"nofollow" class=3D"external tex=
t" href=3D"https://patents.google.com/patent/US1845947">U.S. patent 1,845,9=
47</a></span>) for this device, which performed a 6 =C3=97 6 matrix multipl=
ication modulo 26 using a system of gears and chains.
</p><p>Unfortunately the gearing arrangements (and thus the key) were fixed=
 for any given machine, so triple encryption was recommended for security: =
a secret nonlinear step, followed by the wide diffusive step from the machi=
ne, followed by a third secret nonlinear step. (The much later <a href=3D"h=
ttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Even%E2%80%93Mansour_cipher" class=3D"mw-redir=
ect" title=3D"Even=E2=80=93Mansour cipher">Even=E2=80=93Mansour cipher</a> =
also uses an unkeyed diffusive middle step). Such a combination was actuall=
y very powerful for 1929, and indicates that Hill apparently understood the=
 concepts of a <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meet-in-the-middle_=
attack" title=3D"Meet-in-the-middle attack">meet-in-the-middle attack</a> a=
s well as confusion and diffusion. Unfortunately, his machine did not sell.=
<sup class=3D"noprint Inline-Template Template-Fact" style=3D"white-space:n=
owrap;">[<i><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_nee=
ded" title=3D"Wikipedia:Citation needed"><span title=3D"This claim needs re=
ferences to reliable sources. (September 2020)">citation needed</span></a><=
/i>]</sup>
</p>
